transcript:
Executive: Kya hai? Hello.
Customer: Ha, hello main Himanshu baat kar raha hu IndiaMART se. Good afternoon.
Executive: Haan ji sir boliye.
Executive: Ji ji kal sir call kiya tha na aapne Sunil ko baat discussion ho gayi thi aap se?
Executive: IndiaMART. Accha sir haan ji. Jisne jinhone aap se baat ki thi main unse unka number aapko share kar deti hu. Ek baar aap unse hi baat kar lijiyega.
Executive: Accha accha sir hai nahi kya available? Okay 91 wale number pe.
Executive: Haan ji sir nahi hai aaj.
Executive: 91 wale number se 34 number right?
Executive: 911 haan ji last mein 34 hai unka.
Executive: Accha accha accha. To in services vagaira aap dekhte ho aur sir baki cheeze dekhte hai right?
Executive: Haan IndiaMART ka jo bhi hai ek aap ek
